## Touch Option

Update parent's `updated_at` when child changes.

```ruby
class Comment < ApplicationRecord
  belongs_to :article, touch: true
  # Updates article.updated_at when comment is created/updated/destroyed
end

# Custom attribute to touch
class Comment < ApplicationRecord
  belongs_to :article, touch: :comments_updated_at
  # Updates article.comments_updated_at instead
end
```

